        "markdown": "# Draggable\n\n| | |\n|---|---|\n| **Category** | `Components` |\n| **Tags** | `drag` `headless` `a11y` |\n| **Variants** | 7 |\n\n## Table of Contents\n\n- [Basic](#basic) *(default)*\n- [Multiple draggables](#multiple-draggables)\n- [Spring settle](#spring-settle)\n- [Inside parent bounds](#inside-parent-bounds)\n- [X axis only](#x-axis-only)\n- [Snap to a 24px grid](#snap-to-a-24px-grid)\n- [Activation distance](#activation-distance)\n\n## Variants\n\n### Basic `default`\n\n```vue\n<Draggable class=\"card\">\n  <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n  Drag me — pointer, or Space + arrows\n</Draggable>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Multiple draggables\n\n```vue\n<div class=\"row\">\n  <Draggable class=\"card tone-a\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    One\n  </Draggable>\n  <Draggable class=\"card tone-b\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    Two\n  </Draggable>\n  <Draggable class=\"card tone-c\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    Three\n  </Draggable>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Spring settle\n\n```vue\n<p class=\"hint\">Drag anywhere, then press <kbd>Esc</kbd> — it springs home.</p>\n<Draggable class=\"card\">\n  <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n  Throw me, cancel me\n</Draggable>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Inside parent bounds\n\n```vue\n<div class=\"stage\">\n  <Draggable class=\"card\" bounds=\"parent\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    Bounded\n  </Draggable>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n### X axis only\n\n```vue\n<Draggable class=\"card\" axis=\"x\">\n  <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n  Slides horizontally\n</Draggable>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Snap to a 24px grid\n\n```vue\n<div class=\"stage dotted\">\n  <Draggable class=\"card\" :grid=\"GRID\" bounds=\"parent\">\n    <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    Snaps in steps\n  </Draggable>\n</div>\n```\n\n---\n\n### Activation distance\n\n```vue\n<Draggable class=\"card\" :activation-distance=\"12\">\n  <span class=\"grip\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n  Needs 12px of intent\n</Draggable>\n```\n\n---\n\n## Source\n\n```\n../src/draggable/Draggable.vue\n```\n\n",
