entation=\"horizontal\"\n  :items=\"horizontal\"\n  :item-key=\"trackKey\"\n  @update:items=\"(next) => (horizontal = next)\"\n>\n  <template #item=\"{ item }\">\n    <span class=\"title\">{{ item.title }}</span>\n  </template>\n</SortableList>\n```\n\n---\n\n## Source\n\n```\n../src/sortable/SortableList.vue\n```\n\n",
